701939f-a.title: Bronx: University Avenue - 174th Street (West)
701939f-a.text:
1615 to 1601 University Ave., west side, south from West 175th to
West 174th Streets. On the extreme left, at the S.W. corner of West
174th Street, is visible one of the buildings of the Academy of the
Sacred Heart.
About 1924.
